        <h2 class="text-decoration-underline">Direct Drive That Delivers</h2>
        <p>Simagic's direct drive wheel bases are engineered for ultra-responsive, realistic force feedback that rivals top-tier brands.</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Powerful brushless servo motors with smooth torque delivery</li>
            <li>Low latency and high-resolution FFB signal processing</li>
            <li>Solid aluminum housings for long-term durability</li>
        </ul>
        <br>
        <hr>

        <h2 class="text-decoration-underline">The Alpha Series</h2>
        <p>The Simagic Alpha series covers a range of users—from beginners to esports professionals.</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Alpha Mini</strong> – Compact and affordable, with 10Nm of torque</li>
            <li><strong>Alpha</strong> – Mid-range unit offering 15Nm, ideal for serious sim racers</li>
            <li><strong>Alpha Ultimate</strong> – Delivers 23Nm of torque for high-end competition</li>
        </ul>
        <br>
