        <h2 class="text-decoration-underline">Precision Pedals</h2>
        <p>Simagic pedal sets are designed for adjustability, strength, and precision—perfect for sim racers who demand real-world feedback.</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Available in load cell and hydraulic brake versions</li>
            <li>Fully adjustable pedal spacing, height, and resistance</li>
            <li>Solid steel and aluminum construction for racing longevity</li>
        </ul>
        <br>
