        <p>Simagic’s SimPro Manager software puts tuning and customization at your fingertips, offering detailed control over every aspect of your setup.</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Fine-tune force feedback, pedal curves, and button mappings</li>
            <li>Create and save custom profiles for different cars and games</li>
            <li>Regular firmware and software updates keep hardware optimized</li>
        </ul>
